</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Awards</th>
<td class="infobox-data">
<a href="/wiki/W._J._M._Mackenzie" title="W. J. M. Mackenzie">W. J. M. Mackenzie</a> Prize (1998 and 2016)<br><a href="/wiki/Louis_Brownlow" title="Louis Brownlow">Louis Brownlow</a> Book Award (2015)</td>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1257001546"></td></tr>
<tr><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Academic background</th></tr>
<tr>
